df>

CIO=E2=80=99s tend to like this because it solves the impasse with =
security - put something in the background that satisfies the CISO and =
the chief risk officer (this also mitigates the legal department=E2=80=99s=
 concerns about third party risk), and all the capabilities you want for =
the business can move more quickly into operation.=20



JC


